To release a new version:

Ruby gems
---------
1. Edit lib/icu_tournament/version.rb
2. rake build (check for errors)
3. rake release (if no errors)

Github
------
1. Check all changes into master branch (including version.rb)
2. rake tag
3. rake push

Note - tags are not pushed to github by default. If you want
this then use, for example, git push origin --tags v0.9.6.
